{"tid":2037375,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人政治滿意度跌至新低","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T03:25:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c949796f839e27b4b09820333e9ecfa51e47479a","tid":2037375,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200527/DN7CFHTXQUSQ3UFPG6MWKQSGLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200527%2FDN7CFHTXQUSQ3UFPG6MWKQSGLM%2F&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UxFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=aec6724d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200527%2FDN7CFHTXQUSQ3UFPG6MWKQSGLM%2F&h=50af0568\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200527/DN7CFHTXQUSQ3UFPG6MWKQSGLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n港人政治滿意度跌至新低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YBTE2SEZ22FRCZFPQ2F3L4PPUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYBTE2SEZ22FRCZFPQ2F3L4PPUA.jpg&h=a0f039f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最新民調顯示特首及特區政府的民望仍在低處徘徊。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港民研計劃昨公佈特首及特區政府最新評分，顯示兩者民望都在低處徘徊。不過，市民對現時經濟及政治狀況的滿意淨值大幅下跌，分別為2003年及1992年有紀錄以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n調查在本月19至21日進行，中央出手設港版國安法的消息21日下午才傳出。調查成功訪問1,001名香港居民，結果顯示林鄭最新評分為28.3分，民望淨值為負54個百分點，與半個月前的27.9評分變化不大。。。。。。。。。。。。。滿意淨值都下跌，分別為負61、負66及負86個百分點，當中對經濟狀況的滿意淨值創2003年以來新低，對政治的滿意淨值則較上月大跌11個百分點，創1992年有紀錄以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n48%受訪者予特首0分<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員梁啟智指，15名民主派人士被捕、立法會內會衝突、監警會報告及文憑試歷史科試題等爭議不斷，「咁大堆政治新聞過去兩星期令好多香港人感到好窒息」。他相信數字未反映市民對國安法的意見，相信國安法爭議引發的社會震盪比2003年23條立法更大。對於特首。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁穎妍"},{"pid":"256cbd2917557644806dad4fe9a626fc0e81eb0a","tid":2037375,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"[突發集人］5.27 反國法遊行 1300<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fwPHdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fwPHdS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e6315d9d4acb340a7d8c298bc1356155f9d33c","tid":2037375,"uid":122233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"-86% 有冇detail 正負比率睇睇 真係未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7462251051aa4ad0880c60be759336ec4b4f6519","tid":2037375,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:23:04.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b797061cd2d1cac6a6fa6fb2e3379c34664cc8","tid":2037375,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"有撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人敢怒不敢罷，口屌就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"256cbd2917557644806dad4fe9a626fc0e81eb0a","tid":2037375,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"[突發集人］5.27 反國法遊行 1300<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fwPHdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fwPHdS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}